race.comment: GREY SECRET (8) improving mare who can go on with it now after launching late with a game win over 1425m at this track. Gets map favours today and Buckley sticks. BOMBELLEISTIC (3) produced a reasonable effort with the 59kg when stalked the speed to run third over 1650m at this track. Set to peak third-up and will prove hard to hold out. WRITE YOUR OWN (5) raced without luck in tougher company and undefeated at this track. Kept fresh after fading late when thirteenth to Mount Bona over 1500m at Rosehill in Highway company. Can bounce back today. LINE OF FIRE (1) relished the jump in trip with an improved second over 1600m at Nowra. Capable on his day and the visors go on. Solid top-three prospect.
